{"tid":1357592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗人返唔到屋企關我咩事？","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T18:30:41.000Z","uid":262289,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bab92e840c4fad97b8a2d3d500e360fe620a8e19","tid":1357592,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"反正都當人係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你唔係真係覺得唔關你事啊！！！！！<br />\n人地為香港 出黎遊行完 返屋企就要俾人打 有啲唔關事既市民都打啊 <br />\n警狗已經唔做野啦 我地都乜都唔做 諗住當冇事發生？<br />\n<br />\n而家就係<br />\n中共就lv 100<br />\n港共政府就lv50 <br />\n警狗就lv40<br />\n而班鄉黑就lv20<br />\n<br />\n我地而家連lv20既鄉黑都搞唔撚掂 人地下次仲可以招招積積 橫行無忌咁繼續打 反正我地都唔理啦<br />\n<br />\n元朗班鄉黑都搞唔掂 仲點樣解決港共政府 追究黑警啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597f2f76598e9e455624370c1bd9b94cc142393c","tid":1357592,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講！"},{"pid":"3f244f4de1e153a2ae7510a7c12c9e7ffae05548","tid":1357592,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:05:14.000Z","msg":"我要見律師！"},{"pid":"da92efc7fb5ae42406d55f904bb7bbcda40ab3e9","tid":1357592,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"全世界去元朗遊行！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dc7893037ad01b6f083e86aadb1c1c597d1455","tid":1357592,"uid":262289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:06:56.000Z","msg":"保護市民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef190c360b8cfac4c9a124885309f47db7d24ce","tid":1357592,"uid":282494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"我都覺得要理要追究<br />\n唔理底被人恰<br />\n<br />\n義士要保謢要關註<br />\n遊行人士都要保謢<br />\n<br />\n件事淡化左就好難追究<br />\n好似有人想張件事淡化"},{"pid":"7bf96cb01d06d5454044c9c17767f4ed93107add","tid":1357592,"uid":282494,"like"